1Ô∏è‚É£  Overall architecture
| Layer | What it does | Where it lives |
|-------|--------------|----------------|
| Boot ROM | Reads the 5‚Äëbyte meow.kitten from flash, validates 0x73 checksum from shadow address 0x73. | 0x0000‚ÄØ..‚ÄØ0x07FF (ROM) |
| Vectors & startup | Sets stack, clears BSS, jumps to main(). | 0x0800‚ÄØ..‚ÄØ0x0FFF (flash) |
| Kitten VFS | Creates a 1‚Äëinode ‚Äúfur0‚Äù device, mounts the .kitten file, reports ‚àû‚Äë1 blocks. | RAM (0x2000‚ÄØ..‚ÄØ0x3FFF) |
| Device driver | fur0 ‚Äì a char device that echoes the content of the file to the UART. | MMIO at UARTx->DR (e.g. 0x40021000) |
| Kernel | Idle task = curled tail (WFI), SysTick = purr timer, WDT = yawn. | RAM |
| Init task (cat) | Opens /fur0, prints ‚Äúmeow\n‚Äù. | RAM |
| Build artefacts | One binary kitten.bin that fits in 4‚ÄØKB flash, <‚ÄØ2‚ÄØKB RAM. | ‚Äî |
